{"tid":2361526,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科大學生會：校長變臉令人失望","createTime":"2021-01-10T17:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T00:45:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f1a3555cdef4e9e59f816fe2121452ee4f203d","tid":2361526,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/PRW6OUYSPBEUDBSO2H4OITL7NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FPRW6OUYSPBEUDBSO2H4OITL7NQ%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7fLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=3a1bb8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FPRW6OUYSPBEUDBSO2H4OITL7NQ%2F&h=5982242b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/PRW6OUYSPBEUDBSO2H4OITL7NQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會：校長變臉令人失望<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】儘管死因庭已有裁決，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：街坊：庭上未提關鍵鏡頭被拆<br />\n<br />\n早前在死因庭上作供、時任科大學生會外務副會長梁銘軒（Kelvin）表示，即使事件過去一年多，仍感沉重內疚，因他當時作為學生會幹事有責任照顧同學，但梓樂離世令他感到未能完成使命。Kelvin至今難忘在醫院外守候期間，港人至深夜仍帶心意卡及紙鶴到醫院的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pBIAZcJGA4vkwKhWLHNddJNlxpQ=/1365x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IBRVRXSP45ATTKQLLVFLXT5H5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpBIAZcJGA4vkwKhWLHNddJNlxpQ%3D%2F1365x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIBRVRXSP45ATTKQLLVFLXT5H5E.jpg&h=496fe47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■左起：科大生麥嘉俊、方柏浩及梁銘軒均不滿校方阻撓悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為防暴「開香檳」感氣結<br />\n<br />\n科大學生現任會長麥嘉俊（Donald）表示，梓樂的離世改變了科大向來政治冷感的校園氣氛。原本科大校園內對反送中運動的反響不大，但梓樂離世一事令同學憤怒，「就好似身邊一個同學不明不白咁走咗」，甚至用盡一切方法要求校方回應，曾有同學在畢業禮衝上台要求校長史維表態。但校方冷待事件令一眾同學感無力，「當時聽到校長口口聲聲要為周同學沉冤得雪，但到頭來好似乜都冇做過。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：17歲FA目睹血泊中的梓樂  哭過痛過愧疚過「嚮往周爸爸堅強」<br />\n<br />\n曾有防暴警員在梓樂離世後表示「開香檳慶祝」，Donald至今仍感氣結，「當下聽到會覺得，呢堆人仲可以叫做人咩？」即使政見不同，他也不會輕易說出如此沒人性的說話，至今仍令他感到毛骨悚然。有證人願意在死因庭作供，Donald以為會帶來曙光，但聆訊至尾聲，尚未解答梓樂最後行蹤及其傷勢等疑團。<br />\n<br />\n當時有份籌辦校長論壇的。。。。。。。。。。，令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n科大回應稱，有派員到死因庭旁聽，雖然聆訊未能為周同學的死因釐清所有疑團，但。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3261eb29fa42e7b29471d052f35f30ba069297d6","tid":2361526,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T20:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaa006f44c2fee5e172238721fa919445a5cb90","tid":2361526,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T20:16:16.000Z","msg":"科大咁多已畢業同在讀學生，做校長都唔知要點處理每單離逝case，先令所有人滿意。真難做。"},{"pid":"d1eed29fbcf1fb2d55b24331f0d3d8651949f17e","tid":2361526,"uid":73942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0aaa006f44c2fee5e172238721fa919445a5cb90","tid":2361526,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T20:16:16.000Z","msg":"科大咁多已畢業同在讀學生，做校長都唔知要點處理每單離逝case，先令所有人滿意。真難做。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T00:14:43.000Z","msg":"支那低等生物發現"},{"pid":"1fe60514ff3033b459b0fc4d36f0cc8f3cf67d0c","tid":2361526,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3261eb29fa42e7b29471d052f35f30ba069297d6","tid":2361526,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T20:04:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T00:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}